---
const pageTitle="Luke Amos";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
---
<html lang="en">
	<Header pageTitle={pageTitle} />
	<body>
		<!-- Landing Page -->
		<div class="w-screen h-screen flex items-center justify-center space-x-5 bg-slate-600">
			<div class="w-3/12 flex flex-col">
				<p class="text-white font-heading text-9xl text-center">Hi, I'm <span class="text-green-400">Luke</span></p>
				<p class="text-gray-300 font-body text-4xl text-justify">Give me a problem, no matter how ridiculous, and I will happily sit at my computer for hours on end until I have programmed a solution.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- About Me -->
		<div class="w-screen h-screen flex flex-col items-center">
			<!-- Brief Intro -->
			<div class="w-1/2">
				<p class="text-gray-600 font-heading text-8xl text-center m-10 underline decoration-green-400">About Me</p>
				<div class="w-full flex flex-row space-x-40">
					<div class="w-4/12 flex items-center">
						<img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/006/895/992/small_2x/computer-laptop-cartoon-illustration-icon-with-empty-lcd-panel-vector.jpg">
					</div>
					<div class="w-8/12 flex flex-col text-justify text-gray-600">
						<p class="font-body text-3xl"><strong>It all started with a Minecraft server...</strong></p>
						<p class="font-body text-xl">When I was eight, I had one big problem on my mind: <em>how do I play Minecraft with my friends when they aren't in my house?</em> As I consulted Google, I found a tutorial explaining how to set up a self-hosted Minecraft server. This introduced me to a strange black window lurking inside my Windows 7 machine, and something called a "bat file".</p>
						<p class="font-body text-xl">Since then I have learnt much, and have completed all sorts of projects of varying degrees of usefulness.</p>
						<p class="font-body text-2xl text-right italic transition-all hover:text-green-400 hover:cursor-pointer">Keep Reading</p>
						<br />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Skills -->
			 <div class="w-1/2">
				<p class="text-gray-600 font-heading text-6xl text-left m-10 underline decoration-green-400">My Skills</p>
				<div class="grid-cols"
		
		</div>
	</body>
</html>

